you start wiring up my house.

576
00:38:05,684 --> 00:38:08,246
Why so uptight about
protecting your house from intruders?

577
00:38:08,405 --> 00:38:09,679
Why would you care?

578
00:38:09,844 --> 00:38:11,757
I'm just saying,
it's my house, that's all.

579
00:38:11,925 --> 00:38:14,998
