booby-trapping my house.

580
00:38:15,164 --> 00:38:18,362
Okay, okay. I mean, jeez.
Or as the Germans say, leise...

581
00:38:18,525 --> 00:38:21,085
...which translates to "be cool".
Just be cool.

582
00:38:21,724 --> 00:38:22,954
So, what did you do?

583
00:38:23,125 --> 00:38:26,197
If the front door is opened
while we are in absentia...

584
00:38:26,365 --> 00:38:29,324
...thumbnail-sized, auxiliary,
motion-detector...

585
00:38:29,485 --> 00:38:31,635
...digital-memory cameras
start recording.

586
00:38:31,965 --> 00:38:33,762
You should have told me.

587
00:38:34,085 --> 00:38:37,202
What if they come in through
the back door or the bathroom window...

588
00:38:37,364 --> 00:38:39,003
...like that infamous Beatles' song?

589
00:38:39,164 --> 00:38:41,885
To increase their chances of entering
via the front door...

590
00:38:42,045 --> 00:38:44,719
