591
00:38:44,885 --> 00:38:47,240
...I, fortuitously,
left the front door unlocked.

592
00:38:47,405 --> 00:38:51,159
- Suppose they don't know it's unlocked.
- That's why I left a note on the door.

593
00:38:52,246 --> 00:38:54,396
- You're kidding me.
- No, no. No.

594
00:38:54,565 --> 00:38:57,557
Yes. But no. But yes.

595
00:38:57,724 --> 00:38:59,603
Are you bullshitting us or not?

596
00:38:59,766 --> 00:39:01,916
I just simply never know with you.

597
00:39:02,085 --> 00:39:05,077
- Is he fucking with us, Bob?
- We'll see when we get back.

598
00:39:05,246 --> 00:39:09,204
If there's a note on the door and it's
unlocked, we'll know he isn't lying.

599
00:39:09,365 --> 00:39:11,117
They'd probably take the note down...

600
00:39:11,284 --> 00:39:13,561
...after ripping off
and vandalizing the house...

601
00:39:13,726 --> 00:39:16,159
...and locking the door behind them,
so we don't know.

602
00:39:16,326 --> 00:39:19,204
We will never know.
It's still that gray area.

603
00:39:19,364 --> 00:39:21,833
Of course I'm kidding.
Only a psychotic would do that.

604
00:39:22,005 --> 00:39:24,121
Leave the front door
unlocked with a note on it.

605
00:39:24,286 --> 00:39:25,764
What'd you write
on the note, Jim?

606
00:39:25,925 --> 00:39:28,918
I wrote, "Come on in,
the door's unlocked".

607
00:39:29,365 --> 00:39:31,436
He did it. He really did it.

608
00:39:31,644 --> 00:39:34,398
This is the only way we'll know
for sure who's been doing this.

609
00:39:34,565 --> 00:39:36,920
And is that not what is
of primary importance?

610
00:39:37,085 --> 00:39:40,920
Okay, I'm still gray here.
Now, did you do it or not?

611
00:39:41,085 --> 00:39:42,961
Is it really that suspenseful?

612
00:39:43,126 --> 00:39:45,036
- Did you?
- He did it.

613
00:39:45,204 --> 00:39:46,844
Doesn't matter.
We'll be home shortly.

614
00:39:47,005 --> 00:39:49,041
- Did you?
- We'll be home presently.

615
00:40:32,726 --> 00:40:35,876
Well, Barris, I can see you're right.

616
00:40:36,045 --> 00:40:40,436
This scrupulous covering-over of all
the signs they would've otherwise left...

617
00:40:40,606 --> 00:40:43,643
...testifies to their thoroughness.

618
00:40:43,806 --> 00:40:45,239
You're an idiot.

619
00:40:46,485 --> 00:40:50,195
Oh, wait, wait. This... What's that?

620
00:40:52,085 --> 00:40:54,519
Come here, come here.
Look at this, look at this.

621
00:40:54,806 --> 00:40:58,161
A still-hot cigarette butt. It sure is.
Wait a second.

622
00:40:58,365 --> 00:41:00,596
They lit a joint
while they were here, Bob.

623
00:41:00,766 --> 00:41:03,326
Fuck it. Barris is right,
