627
00:41:12,445 --> 00:41:14,835
- So, what now?
- Maybe they were here specifically...

628
00:41:15,005 --> 00:41:16,724
...to plant drugs in the house.

629
00:41:16,885 --> 00:41:19,161
Setting us up,
then "phoning in a tip" later.

630
00:41:19,326 --> 00:41:21,362
It could be in the phone,
the wall outlets.

631
00:41:21,525 --> 00:41:24,324
We have to go through this house
and get it absolutely clean...

632
00:41:24,485 --> 00:41:26,840
...before they phone us in,
unless they already have.

633
00:41:27,367 --> 00:41:28,559
