634
00:41:29,925 --> 00:41:32,440
You check the wall sockets.
I'll tear this phone apart.

635
00:41:32,606 --> 00:41:34,518
Wait, hold on.
If they see us scrambling...

636
00:41:34,686 --> 00:41:36,166
- ... before the raid...
- What raid?

