we didn't know they were here.

639
00:41:41,646 --> 00:41:47,003
They're going to find us holding them,
or maybe that's part of the plan.

640
00:41:47,525 --> 00:41:50,358
Shit, shit, shit.

641
00:41:50,527 --> 00:41:54,518
We can't do anything.
We're fucked, man. Fuck.

642
00:41:55,806 --> 00:41:57,079
- Fucked, man!
- Barris...

643
00:41:57,246 --> 00:41:59,521
...what about the super-secret
surveillance cameras?

644
00:41:59,686 --> 00:42:02,563
- The what?
- The doodads, man.

645
00:42:02,726 --> 00:42:06,115
Oh, yes, of course. Right, of course.
How could I have forgotten?

646
00:42:06,726 --> 00:42:09,193
