edit yourself out...

708
00:45:36,192 --> 00:45:39,070
...we can deduce who you are through
the process of elimination...

709
00:45:39,233 --> 00:45:40,871
...whether we want to or not.

710
00:45:42,713 --> 00:45:44,226
I'm not sure I exactly...

